Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:



Imprisoner chuckled.  -=Finish her=-


Predator fired off a grenade at Spitfire's chest.

"Choran, you know what to do.  Our plans won't work if these three go talking 
to the Maximals.  Unfortunately for them, none of them have bounties on their 
heads.  Hot Rod would be worth lots of money, but that's probably just some 
want to be robot."

"So, kill them, and we can continue on our way to the Ark."
